abstract: The Kansas City Chiefs are headed to Super Bowl LIV in Miami after ending the Tennessee Titans’ Cinderella-like run in the playoffs with a 35-24 victory.
lead_paragraph: The Kansas City Chiefs are headed to Super Bowl LIV in Miami after ending the Tennessee Titans’ Cinderella-like run in the playoffs with a 35-24 victory at Arrowhead Stadium in the A.F.C. championship game on Sunday.
